Library poplmark.sysf_pat

Require Export fintype.

Section ty.
Inductive ty (pty : scope) : Type :=
  | var_ty : (fin) (pty) → ty (pty)
  | top : ty (pty)
  | arr : ty (pty) → ty (pty) → ty (pty)
  | all : ty (pty) → ty ((Sp) pty) → ty (pty)
  | recty : list (prod (nat ) (ty (pty))) → ty (pty).

Lemma congr_top { qty : scope } : top (qty) = top (qty) .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_arr { qty : scope } { s0 : ty (qty) } { s1 : ty (qty) } { t0 : ty (qty) } { t1 : ty (qty) } (H1 : s0 = t0) (H2 : s1 = t1) : arr (qty) s0 s1 = arr (qty) t0 t1 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_all { qty : scope } { s0 : ty (qty) } { s1 : ty ((Sp) qty) } { t0 : ty (qty) } { t1 : ty ((Sp) qty) } (H1 : s0 = t0) (H2 : s1 = t1) : all (qty) s0 s1 = all (qty) t0 t1 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_recty { qty : scope } { s0 : list (prod (nat ) (ty (qty))) } { t0 : list (prod (nat ) (ty (qty))) } (H1 : s0 = t0) : recty (qty) s0 = recty (qty) t0 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Definition upRen_ty_ty { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) : (fin) ((Sp) (q)) → (fin) ((Sp) (p)) :=
  (up_ren) xi.

Fixpoint ren_ty { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (s : ty (qty)) : ty (pty) :=
    match s return ty (pty) with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ (var_ty (pty)) (xity s)
    | top (_) ⇒ top (pty)
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ arr (pty) ((ren_ty xity) s0) ((ren_ty xity) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ all (pty) ((ren_ty xity) s0) ((ren_ty (upRen_ty_ty xity)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ recty (pty) ((list_map (prod_map (fun x ⇒ x) (ren_ty xity))) s0)
    end.

Definition up_ty_ty { q : scope } { pty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (q) → ty (pty)) : (fin) ((Sp) (q)) → ty ((Sp) pty) :=
  (scons) ((var_ty ((Sp) pty)) (zero)) ((funcomp) (ren_ty (shift)) sigma).

Fixpoint subst_ty { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (s : ty (qty)) : ty (pty) :=
    match s return ty (pty) with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ sigmaty s
    | top (_) ⇒ top (pty)
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ arr (pty) ((subst_ty sigmaty) s0) ((subst_ty sigmaty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ all (pty) ((subst_ty sigmaty) s0) ((subst_ty (up_ty_ty sigmaty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ recty (pty) ((list_map (prod_map (fun x ⇒ x) (subst_ty sigmaty))) s0)
    end.

Definition upId_ty_ty { qty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (qty) → ty (qty)) (Eq : ∀ x, sigma x = (var_ty (qty)) x) : ∀ x, (up_ty_ty sigma) x = (var_ty ((Sp) qty)) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (ap) (ren_ty (shift)) (Eq fin_n)
  | None ⇒ eq_refl
  end.

Fixpoint idSubst_ty { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (qty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, sigmaty x = (var_ty (qty)) x) (s : ty (qty)) : subst_ty sigmaty s = s :=
    match s return subst_ty sigmaty s = s with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ Eqty s
    | top (_) ⇒ congr_top
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_arr ((idSubst_ty sigmaty Eqty) s0) ((idSubst_ty sigmaty Eqty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_all ((idSubst_ty sigmaty Eqty) s0) ((idSubst_ty (up_ty_ty sigmaty) (upId_ty_ty (_) Eqty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ congr_recty ((list_id (prod_id (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (idSubst_ty sigmaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Definition upExtRen_ty_ty { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) (zeta : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) (Eq : ∀ x, xi x = zeta x) : ∀ x, (upRen_ty_ty xi) x = (upRen_ty_ty zeta) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (ap) (shift) (Eq fin_n)
  | None ⇒ eq_refl
  end.

Fixpoint extRen_ty { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (zetaty : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, xity x = zetaty x) (s : ty (qty)) : ren_ty xity s = ren_ty zetaty s :=
    match s return ren_ty xity s = ren_ty zetaty s with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ (ap) (var_ty (pty)) (Eqty s)
    | top (_) ⇒ congr_top
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_arr ((extRen_ty xity zetaty Eqty) s0) ((extRen_ty xity zetaty Eqty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_all ((extRen_ty xity zetaty Eqty) s0) ((extRen_ty (upRen_ty_ty xity) (upRen_ty_ty zetaty) (upExtRen_ty_ty (_) (_) Eqty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ congr_recty ((list_ext (prod_ext (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (extRen_ty xity zetaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Definition upExt_ty_ty { q : scope } { pty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (q) → ty (pty)) (tau : (fin) (q) → ty (pty)) (Eq : ∀ x, sigma x = tau x) : ∀ x, (up_ty_ty sigma) x = (up_ty_ty tau) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (ap) (ren_ty (shift)) (Eq fin_n)
  | None ⇒ eq_refl
  end.

Fixpoint ext_ty { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (tauty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, sigmaty x = tauty x) (s : ty (qty)) : subst_ty sigmaty s = subst_ty tauty s :=
    match s return subst_ty sigmaty s = subst_ty tauty s with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ Eqty s
    | top (_) ⇒ congr_top
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_arr ((ext_ty sigmaty tauty Eqty) s0) ((ext_ty sigmaty tauty Eqty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_all ((ext_ty sigmaty tauty Eqty) s0) ((ext_ty (up_ty_ty sigmaty) (up_ty_ty tauty) (upExt_ty_ty (_) (_) Eqty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ congr_recty ((list_ext (prod_ext (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (ext_ty sigmaty tauty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Definition up_ren_ren_ty_ty { k : scope } { l : scope } { q : scope } (xi : (fin) (k) → (fin) (l)) (tau : (fin) (l) → (fin) (q)) (theta : (fin) (k) → (fin) (q)) (Eq : ∀ x, ((funcomp) tau xi) x = theta x) : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (upRen_ty_ty tau) (upRen_ty_ty xi)) x = (upRen_ty_ty theta) x :=
  up_ren_ren xi tau theta Eq.

Fixpoint compRenRen_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) (rhoty : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (lty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) zetaty xity) x = rhoty x) (s : ty (qty)) : ren_ty zetaty (ren_ty xity s) = ren_ty rhoty s :=
    match s return ren_ty zetaty (ren_ty xity s) = ren_ty rhoty s with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ (ap) (var_ty (lty)) (Eqty s)
    | top (_) ⇒ congr_top
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_arr ((compRenRen_ty xity zetaty rhoty Eqty) s0) ((compRenRen_ty xity zetaty rhoty Eqty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_all ((compRenRen_ty xity zetaty rhoty Eqty) s0) ((compRenRen_ty (upRen_ty_ty xity) (upRen_ty_ty zetaty) (upRen_ty_ty rhoty) (up_ren_ren (_) (_) (_) Eqty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ congr_recty ((list_comp (prod_comp (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (compRenRen_ty xity zetaty rhoty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Definition up_ren_subst_ty_ty { k : scope } { l : scope } { qty : scope } (xi : (fin) (k) → (fin) (l)) (tau : (fin) (l) → ty (qty)) (theta : (fin) (k) → ty (qty)) (Eq : ∀ x, ((funcomp) tau xi) x = theta x) : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (up_ty_ty tau) (upRen_ty_ty xi)) x = (up_ty_ty theta) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (ap) (ren_ty (shift)) (Eq fin_n)
  | None ⇒ eq_refl
  end.

Fixpoint compRenSubst_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) (thetaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (lty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) tauty xity) x = thetaty x) (s : ty (qty)) : subst_ty tauty (ren_ty xity s) = subst_ty thetaty s :=
    match s return subst_ty tauty (ren_ty xity s) = subst_ty thetaty s with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ Eqty s
    | top (_) ⇒ congr_top
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_arr ((compRenSubst_ty xity tauty thetaty Eqty) s0) ((compRenSubst_ty xity tauty thetaty Eqty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_all ((compRenSubst_ty xity tauty thetaty Eqty) s0) ((compRenSubst_ty (upRen_ty_ty xity) (up_ty_ty tauty) (up_ty_ty thetaty) (up_ren_subst_ty_ty (_) (_) (_) Eqty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ congr_recty ((list_comp (prod_comp (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (compRenSubst_ty xity tauty thetaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Definition up_subst_ren_ty_ty { k : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (k) → ty (lty)) (zetaty : (fin) (lty) → (fin) (qty)) (theta : (fin) (k) → ty (qty)) (Eq : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) sigma) x = theta x) : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (ren_ty (upRen_ty_ty zetaty)) (up_ty_ty sigma)) x = (up_ty_ty theta) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (eq_trans) (compRenRen_ty (shift) (upRen_ty_ty zetaty) ((funcomp) (shift) zetaty) (fun x ⇒ eq_refl) (sigma fin_n)) ((eq_trans) ((eq_sym) (compRenRen_ty zetaty (shift) ((funcomp) (shift) zetaty) (fun x ⇒ eq_refl) (sigma fin_n))) ((ap) (ren_ty (shift)) (Eq fin_n)))
  | None ⇒ eq_refl
  end.

Fixpoint compSubstRen_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) (thetaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (lty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) sigmaty) x = thetaty x) (s : ty (qty)) : ren_ty zetaty (subst_ty sigmaty s) = subst_ty thetaty s :=
    match s return ren_ty zetaty (subst_ty sigmaty s) = subst_ty thetaty s with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ Eqty s
    | top (_) ⇒ congr_top
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_arr ((compSubstRen_ty sigmaty zetaty thetaty Eqty) s0) ((compSubstRen_ty sigmaty zetaty thetaty Eqty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_all ((compSubstRen_ty sigmaty zetaty thetaty Eqty) s0) ((compSubstRen_ty (up_ty_ty sigmaty) (upRen_ty_ty zetaty) (up_ty_ty thetaty) (up_subst_ren_ty_ty (_) (_) (_) Eqty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ congr_recty ((list_comp (prod_comp (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (compSubstRen_ty sigmaty zetaty thetaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Definition up_subst_subst_ty_ty { k : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (k) → ty (lty)) (tauty : (fin) (lty) → ty (qty)) (theta : (fin) (k) → ty (qty)) (Eq : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) sigma) x = theta x) : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (subst_ty (up_ty_ty tauty)) (up_ty_ty sigma)) x = (up_ty_ty theta) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (eq_trans) (compRenSubst_ty (shift) (up_ty_ty tauty) ((funcomp) (up_ty_ty tauty) (shift)) (fun x ⇒ eq_refl) (sigma fin_n)) ((eq_trans) ((eq_sym) (compSubstRen_ty tauty (shift) ((funcomp) (ren_ty (shift)) tauty) (fun x ⇒ eq_refl) (sigma fin_n))) ((ap) (ren_ty (shift)) (Eq fin_n)))
  | None ⇒ eq_refl
  end.

Fixpoint compSubstSubst_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) (thetaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (lty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) sigmaty) x = thetaty x) (s : ty (qty)) : subst_ty tauty (subst_ty sigmaty s) = subst_ty thetaty s :=
    match s return subst_ty tauty (subst_ty sigmaty s) = subst_ty thetaty s with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ Eqty s
    | top (_) ⇒ congr_top
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_arr ((compSubstSubst_ty sigmaty tauty thetaty Eqty) s0) ((compSubstSubst_ty sigmaty tauty thetaty Eqty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_all ((compSubstSubst_ty sigmaty tauty thetaty Eqty) s0) ((compSubstSubst_ty (up_ty_ty sigmaty) (up_ty_ty tauty) (up_ty_ty thetaty) (up_subst_subst_ty_ty (_) (_) (_) Eqty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ congr_recty ((list_comp (prod_comp (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (compSubstSubst_ty sigmaty tauty thetaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Definition rinstInst_up_ty_ty { q : scope } { pty : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (pty)) (sigma : (fin) (q) → ty (pty)) (Eq : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (var_ty (pty)) xi) x = sigma x) : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (var_ty ((Sp) pty)) (upRen_ty_ty xi)) x = (up_ty_ty sigma) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (ap) (ren_ty (shift)) (Eq fin_n)
  | None ⇒ eq_refl
  end.

Fixpoint rinst_inst_ty { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (var_ty (pty)) xity) x = sigmaty x) (s : ty (qty)) : ren_ty xity s = subst_ty sigmaty s :=
    match s return ren_ty xity s = subst_ty sigmaty s with
    | var_ty (_) s ⇒ Eqty s
    | top (_) ⇒ congr_top
    | arr (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_arr ((rinst_inst_ty xity sigmaty Eqty) s0) ((rinst_inst_ty xity sigmaty Eqty) s1)
    | all (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_all ((rinst_inst_ty xity sigmaty Eqty) s0) ((rinst_inst_ty (upRen_ty_ty xity) (up_ty_ty sigmaty) (rinstInst_up_ty_ty (_) (_) Eqty)) s1)
    | recty (_) s0 ⇒ congr_recty ((list_ext (prod_ext (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (rinst_inst_ty xity sigmaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Lemma rinstInst_ty { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) : ren_ty xity = subst_ty ((funcomp) (var_ty (pty)) xity) .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun x ⇒ rinst_inst_ty xity (_) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) x)). Qed.

Lemma instId_ty { qty : scope } : subst_ty (var_ty (qty)) = id .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun x ⇒ idSubst_ty (var_ty (qty)) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) ((id) x))). Qed.

Lemma rinstId_ty { qty : scope } : @ren_ty (qty) (qty) (id) = id .
Proof. exact ((eq_trans) (rinstInst_ty ((id) (_))) instId_ty). Qed.

Lemma varL_ty { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) : (funcomp) (subst_ty sigmaty) (var_ty (qty)) = sigmaty .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun x ⇒ eq_refl)). Qed.

Lemma varLRen_ty { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) : (funcomp) (ren_ty xity) (var_ty (qty)) = (funcomp) (var_ty (pty)) xity .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun x ⇒ eq_refl)). Qed.

Lemma compComp_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) (s : ty (qty)) : subst_ty tauty (subst_ty sigmaty s) = subst_ty ((funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) sigmaty) s .
Proof. exact (compSubstSubst_ty sigmaty tauty (_) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) s). Qed.

Lemma compComp'_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) : (funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) (subst_ty sigmaty) = subst_ty ((funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) sigmaty) .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun p ⇒ compComp_ty sigmaty tauty p)). Qed.

Lemma compRen_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) (s : ty (qty)) : ren_ty zetaty (subst_ty sigmaty s) = subst_ty ((funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) sigmaty) s .
Proof. exact (compSubstRen_ty sigmaty zetaty (_) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) s). Qed.

Lemma compRen'_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) : (funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) (subst_ty sigmaty) = subst_ty ((funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) sigmaty) .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun p ⇒ compRen_ty sigmaty zetaty p)). Qed.

Lemma renComp_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) (s : ty (qty)) : subst_ty tauty (ren_ty xity s) = subst_ty ((funcomp) tauty xity) s .
Proof. exact (compRenSubst_ty xity tauty (_) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) s). Qed.

Lemma renComp'_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) : (funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) (ren_ty xity) = subst_ty ((funcomp) tauty xity) .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun p ⇒ renComp_ty xity tauty p)). Qed.

Lemma renRen_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) (s : ty (qty)) : ren_ty zetaty (ren_ty xity s) = ren_ty ((funcomp) zetaty xity) s .
Proof. exact (compRenRen_ty xity zetaty (_) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) s). Qed.

Lemma renRen'_ty { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) : (funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) (ren_ty xity) = ren_ty ((funcomp) zetaty xity) .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun p ⇒ renRen_ty xity zetaty p)). Qed.

End ty.

Section pat.
Inductive pat (pty : scope) : Type :=
  | patvar : ty (pty) → pat (pty)
  | patlist : list (prod (nat ) (pat (pty))) → pat (pty).

Lemma congr_patvar { qty : scope } { s0 : ty (qty) } { t0 : ty (qty) } (H1 : s0 = t0) : patvar (qty) s0 = patvar (qty) t0 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_patlist { qty : scope } { s0 : list (prod (nat ) (pat (qty))) } { t0 : list (prod (nat ) (pat (qty))) } (H1 : s0 = t0) : patlist (qty) s0 = patlist (qty) t0 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Fixpoint ren_pat { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (s : pat (qty)) : pat (pty) :=
    match s return pat (pty) with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ patvar (pty) ((ren_ty xity) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ patlist (pty) ((list_map (prod_map (fun x ⇒ x) (ren_pat xity))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint subst_pat { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (s : pat (qty)) : pat (pty) :=
    match s return pat (pty) with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ patvar (pty) ((subst_ty sigmaty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ patlist (pty) ((list_map (prod_map (fun x ⇒ x) (subst_pat sigmaty))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint idSubst_pat { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (qty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, sigmaty x = (var_ty (qty)) x) (s : pat (qty)) : subst_pat sigmaty s = s :=
    match s return subst_pat sigmaty s = s with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patvar ((idSubst_ty sigmaty Eqty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patlist ((list_id (prod_id (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (idSubst_pat sigmaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint extRen_pat { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (zetaty : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, xity x = zetaty x) (s : pat (qty)) : ren_pat xity s = ren_pat zetaty s :=
    match s return ren_pat xity s = ren_pat zetaty s with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patvar ((extRen_ty xity zetaty Eqty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patlist ((list_ext (prod_ext (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (extRen_pat xity zetaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint ext_pat { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (tauty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, sigmaty x = tauty x) (s : pat (qty)) : subst_pat sigmaty s = subst_pat tauty s :=
    match s return subst_pat sigmaty s = subst_pat tauty s with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patvar ((ext_ty sigmaty tauty Eqty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patlist ((list_ext (prod_ext (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (ext_pat sigmaty tauty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint compRenRen_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) (rhoty : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (lty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) zetaty xity) x = rhoty x) (s : pat (qty)) : ren_pat zetaty (ren_pat xity s) = ren_pat rhoty s :=
    match s return ren_pat zetaty (ren_pat xity s) = ren_pat rhoty s with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patvar ((compRenRen_ty xity zetaty rhoty Eqty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patlist ((list_comp (prod_comp (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (compRenRen_pat xity zetaty rhoty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint compRenSubst_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) (thetaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (lty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) tauty xity) x = thetaty x) (s : pat (qty)) : subst_pat tauty (ren_pat xity s) = subst_pat thetaty s :=
    match s return subst_pat tauty (ren_pat xity s) = subst_pat thetaty s with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patvar ((compRenSubst_ty xity tauty thetaty Eqty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patlist ((list_comp (prod_comp (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (compRenSubst_pat xity tauty thetaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint compSubstRen_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) (thetaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (lty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) sigmaty) x = thetaty x) (s : pat (qty)) : ren_pat zetaty (subst_pat sigmaty s) = subst_pat thetaty s :=
    match s return ren_pat zetaty (subst_pat sigmaty s) = subst_pat thetaty s with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patvar ((compSubstRen_ty sigmaty zetaty thetaty Eqty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patlist ((list_comp (prod_comp (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (compSubstRen_pat sigmaty zetaty thetaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint compSubstSubst_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) (thetaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (lty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) sigmaty) x = thetaty x) (s : pat (qty)) : subst_pat tauty (subst_pat sigmaty s) = subst_pat thetaty s :=
    match s return subst_pat tauty (subst_pat sigmaty s) = subst_pat thetaty s with
    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patvar ((compSubstSubst_ty sigmaty tauty thetaty Eqty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patlist ((list_comp (prod_comp (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (compSubstSubst_pat sigmaty tauty thetaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Fixpoint rinst_inst_pat { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (Eqty : ∀ x, ((funcomp) (var_ty (pty)) xity) x = sigmaty x) (s : pat (qty)) : ren_pat xity s = subst_pat sigmaty s :=

    | patvar (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patvar ((rinst_inst_ty xity sigmaty Eqty) s0)
    | patlist (_) s0 ⇒ congr_patlist ((list_ext (prod_ext (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (rinst_inst_pat xity sigmaty Eqty))) s0)
    end.

Lemma rinstInst_pat { qty : scope } { pty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) : ren_pat xity = subst_pat ((funcomp) (var_ty (pty)) xity) .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun x ⇒ rinst_inst_pat xity (_) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) x)). Qed.

Lemma instId_pat { qty : scope } : subst_pat (var_ty (qty)) = id .
Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun x ⇒ idSubst_pat (var_ty (qty)) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) ((id) x))). Qed.

Lemma rinstId_pat { qty : scope } : @ren_pat (qty) (qty) (id) = id .
Proof. exact ((eq_trans) (rinstInst_pat ((id) (_))) instId_pat). Qed.

Lemma compComp_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) (s : pat (qty)) : subst_pat tauty (subst_pat sigmaty s) = subst_pat ((funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) sigmaty) s .
Proof. exact (compSubstSubst_pat sigmaty tauty (_) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl) s). Qed.

Lemma compComp'_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) : (funcomp) (subst_pat tauty) (subst_pat sigmaty) = subst_pat ((funcomp) (subst_ty tauty) sigmaty) .

Lemma compRen_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) (s : pat (qty)) : ren_pat zetaty (subst_pat sigmaty s) = subst_pat ((funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) sigmaty) s .

Lemma compRen'_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (kty)) (zetaty : (fin) (kty) → (fin) (lty)) : (funcomp) (ren_pat zetaty) (subst_pat sigmaty) = subst_pat ((funcomp) (ren_ty zetaty) sigmaty) .

Lemma renComp_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) (s : pat (qty)) : subst_pat tauty (ren_pat xity s) = subst_pat ((funcomp) tauty xity) s .

Lemma renComp'_pat { kty : scope } { lty : scope } { qty : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (kty)) (tauty : (fin) (kty) → ty (lty)) : (funcomp) (subst_pat tauty) (ren_pat xity) = subst_pat ((funcomp) tauty xity) .

Proof. exact ((FunctionalExtensionality.functional_extensionality _ _ ) (fun p ⇒ renRen_pat xity zetaty p)). Qed.

End pat.

Section tm.
Inductive tm (pty ptm : scope) : Type :=
  | var_tm : (fin) (ptm) → tm (pty) (ptm)
  | app : tm (pty) (ptm) → tm (pty) (ptm) → tm (pty) (ptm)
  | tapp : tm (pty) (ptm) → ty (pty) → tm (pty) (ptm)
  | abs : ty (pty) → tm (pty) ((Sp) ptm) → tm (pty) (ptm)
  | tabs : ty (pty) → tm ((Sp) pty) (ptm) → tm (pty) (ptm)
  | rectm : list (prod (nat ) (tm (pty) (ptm))) → tm (pty) (ptm)
  | proj : tm (pty) (ptm) → nat → tm (pty) (ptm)
  | letpat : ∀ (n : nat), pat (pty) → tm (pty) (ptm) → tm (pty) (Plus n ptm) → tm (pty) (ptm).

Lemma congr_app { qty qtm : scope } { s0 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { s1 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { t0 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { t1 : tm (qty) (qtm) } (H1 : s0 = t0) (H2 : s1 = t1) : app (qty) (qtm) s0 s1 = app (qty) (qtm) t0 t1 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_tapp { qty qtm : scope } { s0 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { s1 : ty (qty) } { t0 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { t1 : ty (qty) } (H1 : s0 = t0) (H2 : s1 = t1) : tapp (qty) (qtm) s0 s1 = tapp (qty) (qtm) t0 t1 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_abs { qty qtm : scope } { s0 : ty (qty) } { s1 : tm (qty) ((Sp) qtm) } { t0 : ty (qty) } { t1 : tm (qty) ((Sp) qtm) } (H1 : s0 = t0) (H2 : s1 = t1) : abs (qty) (qtm) s0 s1 = abs (qty) (qtm) t0 t1 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_tabs { qty qtm : scope } { s0 : ty (qty) } { s1 : tm ((Sp) qty) (qtm) } { t0 : ty (qty) } { t1 : tm ((Sp) qty) (qtm) } (H1 : s0 = t0) (H2 : s1 = t1) : tabs (qty) (qtm) s0 s1 = tabs (qty) (qtm) t0 t1 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_rectm { qty qtm : scope } { s0 : list (prod (nat ) (tm (qty) (qtm))) } { t0 : list (prod (nat ) (tm (qty) (qtm))) } (H1 : s0 = t0) : rectm (qty) (qtm) s0 = rectm (qty) (qtm) t0 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_proj { qty qtm : scope } { s0 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { s1 : nat } { t0 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { t1 : nat } (H1 : s0 = t0) (H2 : s1 = t1) : proj (qty) (qtm) s0 s1 = proj (qty) (qtm) t0 t1 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Lemma congr_letpat { n : nat } { qty qtm : scope } { s0 : pat (qty) } { s1 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { s2 : tm (qty) (Plus n qtm) } { t0 : pat (qty) } { t1 : tm (qty) (qtm) } { t2 : tm (qty) (Plus n qtm) } (H1 : s0 = t0) (H2 : s1 = t1) (H3 : s2 = t2) : letpat (qty) (qtm) n s0 s1 s2 = letpat (qty) (qtm) n t0 t1 t2 .
Proof. congruence. Qed.

Definition upRen_ty_tm { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p) :=
  xi.

Definition upRen_tm_ty { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p) :=
  xi.

Definition upRen_tm_tm { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) : (fin) ((Sp) (q)) → (fin) ((Sp) (p)) :=
  (up_ren) xi.

Definition upRenList_tm_ty (n : nat) { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p) :=
  xi.

Definition upRenList_tm_tm (n : nat) { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) : (fin) (Plus n (q)) → (fin) (Plus n (p)) :=
  upRen_n n xi.

Fixpoint ren_tm { qty qtm : scope } { pty ptm : scope } (xity : (fin) (qty) → (fin) (pty)) (xitm : (fin) (qtm) → (fin) (ptm)) (s : tm (qty) (qtm)) : tm (pty) (ptm) :=
    match s return tm (pty) (ptm) with
    | var_tm (_) (_) s ⇒ (var_tm (pty) (ptm)) (xitm s)
    | app (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ app (pty) (ptm) ((ren_tm xity xitm) s0) ((ren_tm xity xitm) s1)
    | tapp (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ tapp (pty) (ptm) ((ren_tm xity xitm) s0) ((ren_ty xity) s1)
    | abs (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ abs (pty) (ptm) ((ren_ty xity) s0) ((ren_tm (upRen_tm_ty xity) (upRen_tm_tm xitm)) s1)
    | tabs (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ tabs (pty) (ptm) ((ren_ty xity) s0) ((ren_tm (upRen_ty_ty xity) (upRen_ty_tm xitm)) s1)
    | rectm (_) (_) s0 ⇒ rectm (pty) (ptm) ((list_map (prod_map (fun x ⇒ x) (ren_tm xity xitm))) s0)
    | proj (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ proj (pty) (ptm) ((ren_tm xity xitm) s0) ((fun x ⇒ x) s1)
    | letpat (_) (_) n s0 s1 s2 ⇒ letpat (pty) (ptm) n ((ren_pat xity) s0) ((ren_tm xity xitm) s1) ((ren_tm (upRenList_tm_ty n xity) (upRenList_tm_tm n xitm)) s2)
    end.

Definition up_ty_tm { q : scope } { pty ptm : scope } (sigma : (fin) (q) → tm (pty) (ptm)) : (fin) (q) → tm ((Sp) pty) (ptm) :=
  (funcomp) (ren_tm (shift) (id)) sigma.

Definition up_tm_ty { q : scope } { pty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (q) → ty (pty)) : (fin) (q) → ty (pty) :=
  (funcomp) (ren_ty (id)) sigma.

Definition up_tm_tm { q : scope } { pty ptm : scope } (sigma : (fin) (q) → tm (pty) (ptm)) : (fin) ((Sp) (q)) → tm (pty) ((Sp) ptm) :=
  (scons) ((var_tm (pty) ((Sp) ptm)) (zero)) ((funcomp) (ren_tm (id) (shift)) sigma).

Definition upList_tm_ty (n : nat) { q : scope } { pty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (q) → ty (pty)) : (fin) (q) → ty (pty) :=
  (funcomp) (ren_ty (id)) sigma.

Definition upList_tm_tm (n : nat) { q : scope } { pty ptm : scope } (sigma : (fin) (q) → tm (pty) (ptm)) : (fin) (Plus n (q)) → tm (pty) (Plus n ptm) :=
  scons_n n ((funcomp) (var_tm (pty) (Plus n ptm)) (zero_n n)) ((funcomp) (ren_tm (id) (shift_n n)) sigma).

Fixpoint subst_tm { qty qtm : scope } { pty ptm : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (pty)) (sigmatm : (fin) (qtm) → tm (pty) (ptm)) (s : tm (qty) (qtm)) : tm (pty) (ptm) :=
    match s return tm (pty) (ptm) with
    | var_tm (_) (_) s ⇒ sigmatm s
    | app (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ app (pty) (ptm) ((subst_tm sigmaty sigmatm) s0) ((subst_tm sigmaty sigmatm) s1)
    | tapp (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ tapp (pty) (ptm) ((subst_tm sigmaty sigmatm) s0) ((subst_ty sigmaty) s1)
    | abs (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ abs (pty) (ptm) ((subst_ty sigmaty) s0) ((subst_tm (up_tm_ty sigmaty) (up_tm_tm sigmatm)) s1)
    | tabs (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ tabs (pty) (ptm) ((subst_ty sigmaty) s0) ((subst_tm (up_ty_ty sigmaty) (up_ty_tm sigmatm)) s1)
    | rectm (_) (_) s0 ⇒ rectm (pty) (ptm) ((list_map (prod_map (fun x ⇒ x) (subst_tm sigmaty sigmatm))) s0)
    | proj (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ proj (pty) (ptm) ((subst_tm sigmaty sigmatm) s0) ((fun x ⇒ x) s1)
    | letpat (_) (_) n s0 s1 s2 ⇒ letpat (pty) (ptm) n ((subst_pat sigmaty) s0) ((subst_tm sigmaty sigmatm) s1) ((subst_tm (upList_tm_ty n sigmaty) (upList_tm_tm n sigmatm)) s2)
    end.

Definition upId_ty_tm { qty qtm : scope } (sigma : (fin) (qtm) → tm (qty) (qtm)) (Eq : ∀ x, sigma x = (var_tm (qty) (qtm)) x) : ∀ x, (up_ty_tm sigma) x = (var_tm ((Sp) qty) (qtm)) x :=
  fun p ⇒ (ap) (ren_tm (shift) (id)) (Eq p).

Definition upId_tm_ty { qty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (qty) → ty (qty)) (Eq : ∀ x, sigma x = (var_ty (qty)) x) : ∀ x, (up_tm_ty sigma) x = (var_ty (qty)) x :=
  fun p ⇒ (ap) (ren_ty (id)) (Eq p).

Definition upId_tm_tm { qty qtm : scope } (sigma : (fin) (qtm) → tm (qty) (qtm)) (Eq : ∀ x, sigma x = (var_tm (qty) (qtm)) x) : ∀ x, (up_tm_tm sigma) x = (var_tm (qty) ((Sp) qtm)) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (ap) (ren_tm (id) (shift)) (Eq fin_n)
  | None ⇒ eq_refl
  end.

Definition upIdList_tm_ty { n : nat } { qty : scope } (sigma : (fin) (qty) → ty (qty)) (Eq : ∀ x, sigma x = (var_ty (qty)) x) : ∀ x, (upList_tm_ty n sigma) x = (var_ty (qty)) x :=
  fun p ⇒ (ap) (ren_ty (id)) (Eq p).

Definition upIdList_tm_tm { n : nat } { qty qtm : scope } (sigma : (fin) (qtm) → tm (qty) (qtm)) (Eq : ∀ x, sigma x = (var_tm (qty) (qtm)) x) : ∀ x, (upList_tm_tm n sigma) x = (var_tm (qty) (Plus n qtm)) x :=
  fun p ⇒ scons_n_eta (var_tm (qty) (Plus n qtm)) (fun p ⇒ (ap) (ren_tm (id) (shift_n n)) (Eq p)) (fun p ⇒ eq_refl).

Fixpoint idSubst_tm { qty qtm : scope } (sigmaty : (fin) (qty) → ty (qty)) (sigmatm : (fin) (qtm) → tm (qty) (qtm)) (Eqty : ∀ x, sigmaty x = (var_ty (qty)) x) (Eqtm : ∀ x, sigmatm x = (var_tm (qty) (qtm)) x) (s : tm (qty) (qtm)) : subst_tm sigmaty sigmatm s = s :=
    match s return subst_tm sigmaty sigmatm s = s with
    | var_tm (_) (_) s ⇒ Eqtm s
    | app (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_app ((idSubst_tm sigmaty sigmatm Eqty Eqtm) s0) ((idSubst_tm sigmaty sigmatm Eqty Eqtm) s1)
    | tapp (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_tapp ((idSubst_tm sigmaty sigmatm Eqty Eqtm) s0) ((idSubst_ty sigmaty Eqty) s1)
    | abs (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_abs ((idSubst_ty sigmaty Eqty) s0) ((idSubst_tm (up_tm_ty sigmaty) (up_tm_tm sigmatm) (upId_tm_ty (_) Eqty) (upId_tm_tm (_) Eqtm)) s1)
    | tabs (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_tabs ((idSubst_ty sigmaty Eqty) s0) ((idSubst_tm (up_ty_ty sigmaty) (up_ty_tm sigmatm) (upId_ty_ty (_) Eqty) (upId_ty_tm (_) Eqtm)) s1)
    | rectm (_) (_) s0 ⇒ congr_rectm ((list_id (prod_id (fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) (idSubst_tm sigmaty sigmatm Eqty Eqtm))) s0)
    | proj (_) (_) s0 s1 ⇒ congr_proj ((idSubst_tm sigmaty sigmatm Eqty Eqtm) s0) ((fun x ⇒ (eq_refl) x) s1)
    | letpat (_) (_) n s0 s1 s2 ⇒ congr_letpat ((idSubst_pat sigmaty Eqty) s0) ((idSubst_tm sigmaty sigmatm Eqty Eqtm) s1) ((idSubst_tm (upList_tm_ty n sigmaty) (upList_tm_tm n sigmatm) (upIdList_tm_ty (_) Eqty) (upIdList_tm_tm (_) Eqtm)) s2)
    end.

Definition upExtRen_ty_tm { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) (zeta : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) (Eq : ∀ x, xi x = zeta x) : ∀ x, (upRen_ty_tm xi) x = (upRen_ty_tm zeta) x :=
  fun p ⇒ Eq p.

Definition upExtRen_tm_ty { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) (zeta : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) (Eq : ∀ x, xi x = zeta x) : ∀ x, (upRen_tm_ty xi) x = (upRen_tm_ty zeta) x :=
  fun p ⇒ Eq p.

Definition upExtRen_tm_tm { q : scope } { p : scope } (xi : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) (zeta : (fin) (q) → (fin) (p)) (Eq : ∀ x, xi x = zeta x) : ∀ x, (upRen_tm_tm xi) x = (upRen_tm_tm zeta) x :=
  fun p ⇒ match p with
  | Some fin_n ⇒ (ap) (shift) (Eq fin_n)
